Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:09.11,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}后方的正面　{\c&H000000&}抓住这只手的会是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:12.02,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}来　来　过来吧　{\c&H000000&}来跳舞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:14.01,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}比起{\c&H000000&}犹豫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:17.04,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}来　来　过来吧　{\c&H000000&}去寻找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.06,0:02:18.64,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}着急{\c&H000000&}更占多数
