Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.16,0:21:56.95,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Feeling your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:22:00.19,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}人は生まれながら光と影を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:11.50,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}光と影を纏い続ける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.85,0:22:14.26,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Their only one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:19.52,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Feeling your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.59,0:22:22.90,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}欲しいもの全て
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:27.31,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}手に入れること
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.27,0:22:34.21,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}それが幸せなの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:39.12,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}誰かが笑顔なら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.52,0:22:45.49,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}どこかできっと泣いてる人がいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.27,0:22:56.80,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}すれ違うほど　愛おしく思う気持ちがある
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:23:01.68,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}ひとときのあいだに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:08.36,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}僕らはみんな矛盾を抱きしめて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.64,0:23:16.54,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}あしたへの光を見つめながら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.78,0:23:20.86,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}歩いてくのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:22:00.19,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}人类从出生开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:11.50,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}就一直缠绕着光与影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.59,0:22:22.90,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}将一切想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.47,0:22:27.31,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}都收入囊中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.27,0:22:34.21,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那真的就幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:39.12,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}如果有人在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.52,0:22:45.49,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}那一定在某处也有人在哭泣着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.27,0:22:56.80,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}每当擦肩而过 就会觉得怜爱不已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:23:01.68,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}在转瞬而逝的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:08.36,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我们都会怀抱着矛盾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.64,0:23:16.54,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}能够一直看着通向明天的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.78,0:23:20.86,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}一直走下去吗
